      <title>马斯克数十亿美元的薪酬方案激励了其他人。现在该策略受到质疑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/musk-ruling-casts-pall-on-billionaire-spawning-moonshot-awards</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特拉华州法院周二驳回了埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 向特斯拉公司支付 560 亿美元的薪酬方案，这并不是近年来唯一的此类“登月”交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/musk-ruling-casts-pall-on-billionaire-spawning-moonshot-awards</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 20:56:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克薪酬法官猛烈抨击特斯拉董事会“袖手旁观”。这是谁签署的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/musk-pay-judge-slams-supine-tesla-board-here-s-who-signed-off</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拒绝埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 特斯拉公司 (Tesla Inc.) 550 亿美元薪酬方案的法官将批准该方案的董事会比作“傲慢主人的卑鄙仆人”，而不是为股东着想的独立董事。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/musk-pay-judge-slams-supine-tesla-board-here-s-who-signed-off</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 18:20:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前麦格理银行家将领导新的 100 亿美元澳大利亚基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/ex-macquarie-banker-to-lead-10-billion-australia-industry-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[麦格理集团有限公司 (Macquarie Group Ltd.) 的一位前银行家被任命为澳大利亚新设立的 150 亿澳元（100 亿澳元）国家重建基金的首席执行官，该基金是工党政府的一项举措，旨在重振制造业和相关行业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/ex-macquarie-banker-to-lead-10-billion-australia-industry-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
